                        <interp inst="t18350615-name-1024" type="given" value="WILLIAM"></interp>WILLIAM GARRARD</persName>
                  </hi> (<hi rend="italic">police-constable Q</hi> 163.) I found the prisoner on my stairs, held down by the two women—he was very drunk—he said he knew nothing of it—I have heard a good character of him.</p>
